<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-07-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-07-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="107" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d107">
                    <head>No. 413.<lb/><hi rend="italic">General <persName corresp="#p_DES1" type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HF1" type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">United States
                                    Legation in Spain</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-07-24"><hi rend="italic">July</hi> 24, 1873</date>.
                            (Received August 16.)</dateline>
                        <seg rendition="#left">No. 664.]</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The following is a transcript of a cable
                        message I had the honor to send you at 2 o’clock to-day: <quote rend="blockquote">
                            <p><persName corresp="#p_HF1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Hamilton
                                    Fish</hi></persName>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State,
                                    Washington:</hi></p>
                            <p>Minister of finance of new cabinet announced yesterday in Cortes that
                                no reforms would be granted Cuba until insurgents laid down arms.
                                Announcement received with great applause.</p>
                            <p rend="right"><persName corresp="#p_DES1">SICKLES</persName>.</p>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">July</hi> 24.</p>
                        </quote></p>
                    <p>I am, &amp;c.,</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed><persName corresp="#p_DES1">D. E. SICKLES</persName>.</signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>